# Route & Navigation Patterns

## 1. route-adapter 통합 API

라우팅은 `@/shared/libs/route-adapter`의 통합 API만 사용. Standalone(TanStack Router) / Remote(Desktop 탭) 모드를 자동 분기.

```typescript
// ✅ 통합 API import (유일한 방법)
import { useNavigate, useParams, useSearchParams, useLocation, Link, NavLink, Navigate, redirect } from '@/shared/libs/route-adapter';

// ❌ TanStack Router 직접 import 금지
import { useNavigate } from '@tanstack/react-router';

// ❌ react-router-dom 직접 import 금지
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
```

### 네비게이션

```tsx
const navigate = useNavigate();
navigate('/workloads');
navigate(`/workloads/${id}`);
navigate('/workloads', { query: { tab: 'running' } });
```

### 파라미터 추출

```tsx
const { id } = useParams<{ id: string }>();
const [searchParams, setSearchParams] = useSearchParams();
const location = useLocation();
```

### 유틸리티

```tsx
import { buildPath, buildUrl, buildQuery, parseUrl } from '@/shared/libs/route-adapter';
```

---

## 2. RouteConfig 구조

```typescript
import type { RouteConfig } from '@/app/providers/router-provider';

export interface RouteConfig {
  path: string;
  component?: ComponentType | RouteComponent;
  loader?: () => Promise<unknown> | unknown;
  children?: RouteConfig[];
}
```

---

## 3. 라우트 파일 조직

```
app/routes/
├── index.ts                    # LayoutRoutes, AdminRoutes, AuthRoutes 통합
├── main/main.route.ts          # /, /dashboard
├── hub/hub.route.ts            # /ai-models, /datasets, /packages, /benchmarks
├── infrastructure/             # /workloads, /my-templates, /volumes, /serverless
├── ml-studio/                  # /dev-spaces, /text-generation, /tabular
├── mlops/                      # /pipelines, /monitoring
├── operations/                 # /cluster-management, /kueue
├── settings/                   # /settings, /projects, /groups
├── auth/                       # /login, /signup
├── admin/                      # /admin/*
├── error/                      # /404 (catch-all)
└── remote/                     # Desktop 모드 VirtualRoute 레지스트리
```

### 도메인 → 카테고리 매핑 기준

| 카테고리 | 도메인 | 기준 |
|----------|--------|------|
| hub | ai-models, datasets, packages, benchmarks | 공유 리소스/허브 |
| infrastructure | workloads, templates, volumes, serverless | 인프라/컴퓨팅 |
| ml-studio | dev-spaces, text-generation, tabular | ML 개발 도구 |
| mlops | pipelines, monitoring | ML 운영/파이프라인 |
| operations | cluster-management, kueue | 클러스터 운영 |
| settings | settings, projects, groups, users | 설정/관리 |

